headline: Synchrony to Participate in the Barclays Global Financial Services Conference
summary: Synchrony (NYSE: SYF) Chief Financial Officer, Brian J. Wenzel, will participate in a fireside chat at the Barclays Global Financial Services Conference on Wednesday, September 10, 2025 at 7:30 a.m. (Eastern Time).
